field4:
Hello,

We are a company currently preparing to launch a pharmaceutical dropshipping platform targeting the Korean market.
Our top priority is to provide customers with reliable products in a fast and secure manner.
To achieve this, we are actively seeking trustworthy suppliers with whom we can build a long-term, mutually beneficial partnership.

We greatly value the strength of your products and distribution capabilities,
and we hope to establish a cooperative relationship that allows both parties to grow together.
In return, we are committed to conducting all business with honesty, transparency, and a strong sense of responsibility.

We would sincerely appreciate it if you could review the attached supplier response request form,
and we look forward to hearing your positive consideration regarding a potential partnership.

As pharmaceuticals have a direct impact on the human body,
consumers are highly sensitive to whether the ingredients are accurate and the effectiveness of the product is proven.
Even the slightest suspicion can lead to immediate claims, refund requests, or formal complaints.

In the Korean market in particular, it is critically important that the listed ingredients match the actual contents,
and that the products are not ineffective or counterfeit medications.

In light of this, we strictly work only with suppliers who can guarantee that their products contain the stated ingredients
and have verified efficacy.

Could you kindly confirm that the products you supply meet these standards
and can be guaranteed to be genuine medicines with verified ingredients and effects?

Please review the product list below and check the items your company is able to supply.
If possible, kindly fill in the supply price for each item (including shipping to Korea) on the corresponding row.

If there are too many items to list prices for all,
you may simply mark the products you are able to supply.
We will use this information as a reference and reach out individually for further discussion.

That said, suppliers who are able to provide full responses—including pricing—may be prioritized for earlier partnership opportunities.

Please note that there may be some inaccuracies in the product or ingredient names.
To minimize any confusion, we have included reference images for each product,
so we kindly ask that you refer to the images for accurate identification before filling out the form.

Thank you very much.
